description:
Forget all the political bullshit that can be said for what’s gone on since C19 impacted our everyday lives

You can either play the victim game, use the virus, blame the political climate, use the fact gyms are closed

Or

You can look yourself in the mirror and except the fact the only thing that’s stopped you from becoming a better version of yourself....is yourself

There will ALWAYS be reasons why it’s hard

The vast majority of us are NOT in the perfect situation to do everything we want all the time

BUT

The truth is, the vast majority of us have the ability to make decisions, time and all the resources we need

We just need the heart, willingness, discipline and effort

Stop worrying about what you “can’t” and simply start doing

And yes, it is that easy

#itsnotthemitsyou
#beyourbestself
#maninthemirror
#youcontrolyou
#doitanyway
#teamrowanfitness
